      "cookedHtml": "<h1><a name=\"p-239467-weve-just-rolled-out-an-optimized-social-media-calendar-board-view-for-publisher-social-media-app-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-239467-weve-just-rolled-out-an-optimized-social-media-calendar-board-view-for-publisher-social-media-app-1\"></a><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=15\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />We’ve just rolled out an optimized Social Media Calendar Board View for Publisher: Social Media app  <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=15\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></h1>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/f/5f285c01d3da7e9bcf5968b8f4564e986517975f.jpeg\" title=\"gloabl-2\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/f/5f285c01d3da7e9bcf5968b8f4564e986517975f_2_690x388.jpeg\" alt=\"gloabl-2\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">gloabl-2</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1080 424 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Now, managing your social media schedules is even smoother and more intuitive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Get a clear calendar overview of your social media posts directly from your board<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Navigate and plan content faster with improved performance<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Stay on top of all your publishing timelines in one place</p>\n<p>Here’s what you’ll get:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/date.png?v=15\" title=\":date:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":date:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Board-scoped schedules</strong> – view posts only for the board you’re working in.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/framed_picture.png?v=15\" title=\":framed_picture:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":framed_picture:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Optimized visibility</strong> – see media thumbnails, post copy snapshots, and the targeted social platform right in your calendar.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/artist_palette.png?v=15\" title=\":artist_palette:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":artist_palette:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Clear status icons</strong> – color-coded symbols for <strong>Scheduled, Published, Incomplete,</strong> and <strong>Failed</strong> posts.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/spiral_calendar.png?v=15\" title=\":spiral_calendar:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":spiral_calendar:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Flexible views</strong> – switch easily between <strong>Month view</strong> and <strong>Week view</strong>.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/magnifying_glass_tilted_left.png?v=15\" title=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":magnifying_glass_tilted_left:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>Smart filtering</strong> – filter posts by <strong>accounts, platforms, or labels</strong> to stay focused.</p>\n<p>This makes planning and monitoring your social media campaigns smoother than ever — right inside your <a>monday.com</a> board.</p>\n<p><strong>Get Yours Now</strong> <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_down.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_down.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/backhand_index_pointing_down.png?v=15\" title=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":backhand_index_pointing_down:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> <strong>:</strong></p>\n<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/d/dd4cf2ca4142e9b9bbb7fb50954ca95b2c203dfa.png\" class=\"site-icon\" alt=\"\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\" />\n\n      <a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000827/social-media---publisher?utm_source=community&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=publisher_features&amp;utm_content=optimized-calendar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    \n\n<h3><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000827/social-media---publisher?utm_source=community&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=publisher_features&amp;utm_content=optimized-calendar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Social Media - Publisher - monday.com Marketplace</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Social Media Integration, Automation, Planning &amp; Scheduling.</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div></div>\n</aside>\n\n<ul>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Publisher is a <a>monday.com</a> app that lets you plan, create, and publish social media content directly from your boards — with multi-channel support, scheduling, and campaign management all in one place, <strong><a href=\"https://monday.com/marketplace/listing/10000827/social-media---publisher?utm_source=community&amp;utm_medium=post&amp;utm_campaign=publisher_features&amp;utm_content=optimized-calendar#\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">all without leaving monday.com</a></strong>.*<br />\n<a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/facebook\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>facebook</span></a> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#instagram</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#linkedin</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#tiktok</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#threads</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#youtube</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#pinterest</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#bluesky</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#mastodon</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#X</span>(twitter)</p>"
